 "contentEncoded": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/35762610@N03/5258234535/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5082/5258234535_f4d6816515.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"400\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Good morning, Nashville. You might have noticed that&#x2019;s snowing outside! <a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20110110/NEWS01/110110003/-1/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Most of Nashville received anywhere from 2-4&#x2033; last night</a>, resulting in <a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/closings/index.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">school closures</a>, <a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/politics/26425860/detail.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">canceled flights</a>, <a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/Global/story.asp?S=13814388\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">hazardous driving conditions</a> and an <a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/weather/26420801/detail.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">official state of emergency</a>. According to weather forecasts, we&#x2019;ve probably got <a href=\"http://nashvillewx.com/2011/01/updated-snow-forecast-for-today-more-on-the-way-tomorrow/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillewx.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">another inch or two on the way tonight into tomorrow</a>. We can has snow day?</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Inauguration time. </strong>Governator-to-be Bill Haslam<a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/Global/story.asp?S=13814681\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\"> kicks off his inauguration festivities this week with a tour around the state leading up to his inauguration ceremony on Friday night</a>.</li>\n<li><strong>Less green, more roof. </strong>Developers <a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20110109/NEWS01/101090363/-1/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">had to slash part of the green roof plans for the Music City Center in order to stay within budget</a>. With the new plan, greenery will cover about 28% of the roof&#x2019;s surface.</li>\n<li><strong>Bits &amp; pieces. </strong><a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/story/13813731/mta-buses-operate-on-snow-routes-monday\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">MTA buses will be running on snow routes</a> today and probably also tomorrow &#x2026; <a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/story/13812731/nes-offers-reprieve-during-bitterly-cold-temperatures\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">NES suspends energy disconnections for folks who can&#x2019;t pay their bills</a> when temperatures drop below freezing &#x2026; <a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/Global/story.asp?S=13812468\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Bud Adams really wanted to keep Vince Young and Coach Fisher</a>, but &#x201C;couldn&#x2019;t find a way to make the relationship work&#x201D; &#x2026; Fort Campbell&#x2019;s 101st Air Division <a href=\"http://www.fox17.com/template/inews_wire/wires.regional.tn/21daaefc-www.fox17.com.shtml\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.fox17.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">has had its deadliest combat year since Vietnam</a> &#x2026; <a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/entertainment/26417300/detail.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">A fire destroyed Charlie Daniels&#x2019; barn over the weekend</a> and killed 11 horses &#x2026; <a href=\"http://www.fox17.com/template/inews_wire/wires.regional.tn/25daba33-www.fox17.com.shtml\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.fox17.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Former Congressman Zach Wamp&#x2019;s father has died</a> after falling at his office in Chattanooga.</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>Photo by <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/35762610@N03/5258234535/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Katety Allen</a>.</em></p>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2008/11/21/bright-early-tut-tut-looks-like-snow/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Bright &amp; Early: Tut Tut, Looks Like&#x2026; Snow?\">Bright &amp; Early: Tut Tut, Looks Like&#x2026; Snow?</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2010/01/06/bright-early-doing-our-snow-dance-edition/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Bright &amp; Early: Doing Our Snow Dance Edition\">Bright &amp; Early: Doing Our Snow Dance Edition</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2010/06/04/bright-early-donuts-on-the-brain-edition/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Bright &amp; Early: Donuts On The Brain Edition\">Bright &amp; Early: Donuts On The Brain Edition</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2009/02/23/bright-early-fierce-competition-edition/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Bright &amp; Early: Fierce Competition Edition\">Bright &amp; Early: Fierce Competition Edition</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2011/01/06/bright-early-clash-of-the-titans-edition/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Bright &amp; Early: Clash Of The Titans Edition\">Bright &amp; Early: Clash Of The Titans Edition</a></li>\n</ol></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"
